  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study is not hypothesis driven but will explore the ability of
      pharmacokinetic-pharmacodynamic modelling to predict optimal dosage of the chemotherapeutic
      drugs used in therapy in adult patients with acute myeloid leukemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
